{"tid":1169048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龍緯汶涉狎女童拍親暱照 警調查後揭疑至少有四名受害人","createTime":"2019-05-24T06:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T06:29:24.000Z","uid":64948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a03aa0024a38fbc915c5e0825003059f42f10f17","tid":1169048,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190524/59635436?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ygwDJPV74Sz_ztNj6Dm3hImYaxt-7e9wiI2vpdZ-Tfgaw1Ob0P3DkgNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190524%2F59635436%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ygwDJPV74Sz_ztNj6Dm3hImYaxt-7e9wiI2vpdZ-Tfgaw1Ob0P3DkgNU&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=51e5ed71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190524%2F59635436%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ygwDJPV74Sz_ztNj6Dm3hImYaxt-7e9wiI2vpdZ-Tfgaw1Ob0P3DkgNU&h=5b8c5b9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190524/59635436?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ygwDJPV74Sz_ztNj6Dm3hImYaxt-7e9wiI2vpdZ-Tfgaw1Ob0P3DkgNU</a><br />\n<br />\n關注少數族裔權益組織、「南方民主同盟」主席龍緯汶涉與至少兩名少數族裔女童拍下親暱合照，及後他被控非禮及藏有兒童色情物品等五罪。控方早前提堂時透露，除了控罪提及的兩名女童外，另有一名6歲的潛在女受害人；案件今再訊時，控方指警方再找到另一名同為6歲的非華裔潛在受害人，惟女童父母不在港，警方需時約見女童及其父母，以及調查是否再有其他受害人。裁判官將案件押後至下月26日再訊。聆訊期間一直「頭耷耷」的龍緯汶沒有保釋申請，繼續還押監房候訊。<br />\n現年44歲的龍緯汶報稱社工，惟根據社工註冊局網上資料顯示，註冊社工名單上並無被告資料。龍緯汶現被控兩項非禮、兩項向年齡在16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為，以及一項管有兒童色情物品罪，涉及兩名未滿16歲女童。<br />\n案件於本周一首次提堂，控方當時透露，除女童X和Y外，警方在被告的手機內找到另一名6歲女童的相片。控方今早稱，警方已完成相關認人手續，Y未能認出被告，但Y的母親認到被告。至於6歲女童，警方已向她錄取口供，但她未能說出實際情況。<br />\n被告現面對的控罪，指他於今年3月至4月期間，在旺角某一工業大廈內兩度非禮女童X，又於2017年至2018年間，分別在泳池更衣室內以及其住所內，向女童X及女童Y作出嚴重猥褻行為，兩名女童當時均不足16歲。控罪另指，被告於本月17日在住所內管有19張兒童色情照片和一段兒童色情影片。<br />\n【案件編號：KCCC1427/19】<br />\n記者戴國輝"},{"pid":"0c508c2ed8da270dfe5016ed66c84c4d6ced14fd","tid":1169048,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"150daa8a598b7c0d0d98e182dd1f49b18abd7918","tid":1169048,"uid":109136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"泳池更衣室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9a1edb1e8ae4a6e79e51e9648ecd11a94a2eaa","tid":1169048,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"古天樂張國榮blah blah blah"},{"pid":"2ed3b6f618a0bd8bbd28ba7594b4d10be4eee632","tid":1169048,"uid":59283,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"現年44歲的龍緯汶報稱社工，惟根據社工註冊局網上資料顯示，註冊社工名單上並無被告資料。<br />\n又衰多瓣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1713d9505c67eb771fd535372ca2825fd40711","tid":1169048,"uid":237425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2ed3b6f618a0bd8bbd28ba7594b4d10be4eee632","tid":1169048,"uid":59283,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"現年44歲的龍緯汶報稱社工，惟根據社工註冊局網上資料顯示，註冊社工名單上並無被告資料。<br />\n又衰多瓣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"吊啦星原來條淫棍係無牌社工<br />\n係唔係會罰得再重D?"},{"pid":"db39d8f42e11b9c23741d81bc99e2e8187927056","tid":1169048,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bd81b374ba37ee0e9c2e2c3fc22f67b994cc4e","tid":1169048,"uid":83328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quo